node.text:
The highlight of 2020 for me was launching a business that marries my passion for medicine and beauty all rolled into one. That’s why I’m happy to announce that my brand @muze.labs will now be available at @musclelab. If you drop by the facility to workout or rehab, make sure to grab some wipes💧

It was important to find a brand that aligns with our mission to promote a healthy lifestyle for all people. Whether it’s skin care or fitness, it’s all about self care. Make this upcoming year about bettering yourself in all aspects. Muze does it all, because you do it all 🦾

Use my code “ROBIN20” at checkout for 20% off your purchase! 💤 #ad

node.text:
— No competition, no progress!☝🏽 @buffbunny_collection 

The pharmacy job market is extremely competitive with over 14,000 pharmacy school graduates each year and next to no new position openings 🤯

It can seem impossible to land a job, but don’t forget to explore other fields of pharmacy that might interest you.

Really soak in your experiences on rotations as a 4th year pharmacy student, you never know what may spark your interest! 

#drrobinb #phashionpharmacist #fitness #buffbunnycollection #prettylittledoctor
